oyees. 77% of its customers are postpaid customers while 15% and 8% are prepaid customers and wholesale</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1431042152/image_1431042152.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741505-t-mobile-stock-further-growth-shareholder-returns-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:45:09"}, {"id": "4741504", "title": "Columbia Sportswear: Undervalued, Positioned For Growth", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Men\"s Jogging supplies shot knolling style.' data-id=\"641229891\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5786px\" height=\"4353px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yagi Studio</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>In my view, Columbia Sportswear (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COLM\" title=\"Columbia Sportswear Company\">COLM</a></span>) has a lot of tailwinds ahead with reasonably priced clothing and great fabric technologies. The company also has performed subpar in recent years, with below-average financial growth across many metrics. Though has a strong</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/641229891/image_641229891.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741504-columbia-sportswear-undervalued-positioned-for-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:38:17"}, {"id": "4741502", "title": "Qualcomm: Auto Business Offers Material Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Qualcomm Snapdragon MSM7227A\" data-id=\"1196326348\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">G0d4ather</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Qualcomm\u2019s (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QCOM\" title=\"QUALCOMM Incorporated\">QCOM</a></span>) automotive business has gone from strength to strength in recent years and is now an important value driver for the company. This opportunity is just beginning though, as the introduction of more advanced ADAS/AV solutions will significantly</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326348/image_1196326348.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741502-qualcomm-auto-business-offers-material-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:30:17"}, {"id": "4741500", "title": "Pembina Pipeline: Low-Risk Dividend Play. Series 5 Preferreds Offer Competitive Yield", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Road Construction\" data-id=\"184641800\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">kozmoat98/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Investment case</strong></h2> <p>The election of Donald Trump as the next US president will likely become a significant tailwind to Canadian energy and midstream companies. The new US president seems focused on lowering energy costs to minimize</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184641800/image_184641800.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741500-pembina-pipeline-low-risk-dividend-play-series-5-preferreds-offer-competitive-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 18:15:48"}, {"id": "4741497", "title": "Drill, Baby, Drill - But Buy ENFR Instead Of The Drillers", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157307794/image_157307794.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oilfield\" data-id=\"157307794\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1028px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157307794/image_157307794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157307794/image_157307794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157307794/image_157307794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.