seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kevin Burkholder</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Boeing (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BA\" title=\"The Boeing Company\">BA</a></span>) is working on a huge turnaround, which amongst other things, includes stabilizing production, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732814-boeing-sell-the-defense-and-space-businesses\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732814-boeing-sell-the-defense-and-space-businesses\" target=\"_blank\">selling non-core businesses</a> and <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4730162-boeing-a-6-billion-loss-was-hardly-a-surprise-neither-was-the-22-billion-capital-raise\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4730162-boeing-a-6-billion-loss-was-hardly-a-surprise-neither-was-the-22-billion-capital-raise\" target=\"_blank\">improving liquidity to address debt maturities</a> in the years ahead. All of this should result in better free cash</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2140609451/image_2140609451.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741496-boeing-selling-the-83-billion-inventories-is-essential-to-a-stronger-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 17:58:29"}, {"id": "4741492", "title": "TCW Select Equities Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Four hands taking slices of a pie chart\" data-id=\"1824400059\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Performance</h2> <p>The Fund (I Share) generated a net return of +1.41% during the third quarter, underperforming the Russell 1000 Growth Index return of +3.19%. Relative underperformance was primarily due to negative security selection effects (primarily in the information technology, consumer discretionary and industrials sectors). YTD through the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824400059/image_1824400059.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741492-tcw-select-equities-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 17:34:00"}, {"id": "4741447", "title": "SCHD Is Both Cheap And Good", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pink piggy banks on ascending stacks of paper currency\" data-id=\"1398472101\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1008px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398472101/image_1398472101.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px)